lead_paragraph: James Harden scored 35 points and Trevor Ariza added a season-high 31 to help the hot-shooting Houston Rockets beat the short-handed New Orleans Pelicans 112-111 on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Harden and Ariza Lead Rockets to 112-111 Win Over Pelicans
